HEADWORD: Nestor
<hw>Nes"tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A genus of parrots with gray heads, of New Zealand and Papua,
allied to the cockatoos. See <er>Kaka</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nestorian</ent>⟦br⟧
